item.title: ProfitPeak
item.description: A chrome extension that allows users to view their “Profit and Loss” of crypto swaps and track wallet gains. I developed the full frontend, storage solutions, and integrating custom API wrappers. This extension was created by Marc Vaz, Ahmed Abidallah, Chelsea Pan, and Rayyan Shaik.
